<div class="main-content">
  <div class="keep-in-mind">
    <div class="sec-title">
      <h2>THINGS TO REMEMBER</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="rules">
      <div class="column">
        <div>
          <h3 style="text-transform:uppercase">The Mokae Pro Code</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Use your Pro discount for your kit—and yes, to treat yourself too.</li>

            <li>We’d love to see your artistry, reviews, and behind-the-scenes shared with the Mokae community.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div>
          <h3 style="text-transform:uppercase">Code of Conduct</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Mokae Pro discounts are intended for personal professional use only—not for resale or bulk purchasing.
            </li>
            <li>
              Please don’t share your Pro code publicly or with non-members. Misuse may lead to removal from the
              program.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cta">
      <h4 style="text-transform:uppercase">Apply for the Mokae Pro Circle</h4>
      <p>
        Join a growing collective of artists shaping the future of beauty. If you’re ready to step in, we’re ready to
        welcome you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .main-content {
    background: #fff;
    color: #111;
  }

  .sec-title h2 {
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .keep-in-mind {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .keep-in-mind h2 {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .rules {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: stretch;
    width: min(100%, 720px);
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .rules {
      flex-direction: row;
    }

    .rules .column {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 2rem 3rem 0;
      padding-bottom: 0rem;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .rules .column:first-child {
      border-left: none;
    }

    .rules .column:last-child {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }

  .rules h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .rules ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .rules ul li {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1vw;
  }

  .cta h4 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .cta p {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (min-width: 20px) and (max-width: 600px) {
    .cta * {
      text-align: left !important;
    }

    .sec-title h2 {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .keep-in-mind {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 5rem 4rem;
    }

    .keep-in-mind h2 {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }

    .rules {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: stretch;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2vw;
      border-top: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .rules h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .rules ul li {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 5vw;
    }

    .rules ul li br {
      display: none;
    }

    .column:first-child {
      margin-bottom: 8vw;
      padding-bottom: 8vw;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .cta h4 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta p {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .cta p br {
      display: none;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>

